snippet.title: Super Mario Sunshine Seaside - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Mario Sunshine Seaside is my upcoming mod of New Super Mario Bros. U for Wii U.
In this 1-world mod, Mario ventures off to a sunny tropical island, exploring 8 unique levels in his quest to defeat Bowser Jr.
Fittingly, I am hoping to release this mod this summer, so stay tuned!

The trailer was recorded and edited by @Rimea, the trailer theme was created by @bunten which is also part of the mod's soundtrack!

This trailer was also shown in the New Super Mario Bros. Franchise Modding Direct by Rimea: https://youtu.be/dvAH9bEEuPk

Sunshine Seaside's Gamebanana Page: https://gamebanana.com/wips/67330
